descriptions.Description: The Hobbit is a series of three epic high fantasy adventure films directed by Peter Jackson. The films are subtitled An Unexpected Journey, The Desolation of Smaug, and The Battle of the Five Armies. The films are based on the 1937 novel The Hobbit by J. R. R.
